        <section name="scala-maven-plugin">
            <p>The scala-maven-plugin is used for compiling/testing/running/documenting scala code in maven.</p>
            <p>If there are problems please let us know.</p>
        </section>
        <section name="Requirements">
            <ul>
                <li>Maven 3.0+</li>
                <li>JDK 1.5</li>
                <li><bold>No need to install <a href="http://scala-lang.org">scala</a> !</bold></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
